The overall impression would be one of order and symmetry, with the rectangular and triangular panels arranged in a precise and carefully calculated pattern. The circular window above the entrance, with its geometric pattern of dark gray metal, would provide a focal point for the composition, drawing the viewer's eye upwards towards the sky.
